<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>OTP Verification</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6a11cb 0%, #2575fc 100%);
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #333333;
    }
    .container {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 50px auto;
      padding: 40px 30px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
      text-align: center;
    }
    h2 {
      color: #1a1a1a;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 28px;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 17px;
      color: #555555;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 16px 0;
    }
    .otp-code {
      margin: 30px auto;
      padding: 18px 50px;
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: #ffffff;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #2575fc, #6a11cb);
      border-radius: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 8px;
      width: fit-content;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(38, 61, 183, 0.5);
      user-select: all;
    }
    .footer {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #999999;
      margin-top: 40px;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      padding-top: 20px;
      font-style: italic;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Hello <%= name %>,</h2>
    <p>We received a request to verify your identity. Please use the following OTP code to complete the verification process:</p>
    <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>
    <p>This code is valid for <strong>3 minutes</strong>. If you didnâ€™t request this, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
    <p>Thank you,<br />The LoopRide Support Team</p>
    <div class="footer">
      &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> LoopRide. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
